  "instructions": [
    "Combine coconut milk, gochujang, and miso paste in a saucepan over medium heat, whisking until smooth.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 5-7 minutes or until slightly thickened.",
    "Stir in saeujeot-shrimp-paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add lime juice and season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Meanwhile, grill the shrimp for 2-3 minutes per side or until fully cooked.",
    "Arrange the cooked Japanese rice in the lacquerware bowl, topping with grilled shrimp, pickled ginger, and crushed sesame seeds.",
    "Drizzle the coconut cream-crack over the top and garnish with fresh cilantro.",
    "Finish by sprinkling cracked coconut flakes over the dish and serving immediately.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro and sesame seeds if desired."
